Package seng202.team5.model

Class FlightModel

java.lang.Object
seng202.team5.model.FlightModel
public class FlightModel
extends java.lang.Object
FlightModel Model class for flights, used as the object by PropertyValueFactories in the flight table. Consists of only a constructor, getters and setters.
